{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c0ca95cf55","title":"在黄镇关于印尼寻求贷款问题的报告上的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cbc0e952dc","index":0,"year":1958,"month":7,"day":31,"articleId":"c0ca95cf55"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji39","name":"毛泽东全集第39卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/39-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji39":{"comments":[{"id":"59dc2484a7","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"黄镇，当时任中国驻印度尼西亚大使。"},{"id":"d4c282fdef","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"陈毅，当时任国务院副总理兼外交部部长。"},{"id":"14eaf94aca","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指黄镇1958年7月27日给外交部的报告。其中第二页上说，根据印尼向苏联要求贷款的情况，以及印尼当前继续执行镇压颠覆活动的政策，要取得美国的贷款尚有许多困难，印尼既已向我政府道切地提出了贷款的要求，我馆意见，我政府可量贷予一部分。这将和过去的米、布贷款一样，会起到雪中送炭的作用。"}],"contents":[{"id":"92591ddadd","type":"title","text":"在黄镇关于印尼寻求贷款问题的报告上的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55"},{"id":"59dc2484a7","type":"paragraph","text":"陈毅同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55"},{"id":"d4c282fdef","type":"paragraph","text":"此件以第二页第二段所说向我贷款事，黄镇是否曾有报告？如有，请送一阅。此件阅后退毛。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55"},{"id":"14eaf94aca","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55"},{"id":"d4a2d1c1da","type":"paragraph","text":"七月册一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55"}],"page":{"id":"0fbaa3d8b9","publicationId":"maoquanji39","articleId":"c0ca95cf55","start":513,"end":513}}}},"__N_SSG":true}